<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/11 (Thu.) The world after Covid19/ table topics (Host:　Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=479&amp;p=501#p501"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #FF0000">Place: 丹堤咖啡, 台北市延平南路107號2樓 (MRT 西門站4號出口)<br />Agenda: The world after Covid19/ table topics (Host:　Lawrence)<br /><br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks <br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2 Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation</span><br /><br />Session 1: How does Covid19 affect us in the long term?<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20200629-which-lockdown-changes-are-here-to-stay">https://www.bbc.com/future/article/2020 ... re-to-stay</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. Would you take the vaccine against Covid19? Why or why not?<br />2. Can you predict what the world will be like all over the world after this pandemic?<br />3. How does it change your way of life?<br />4. How does it change your perspective on life, for example, life so unpredictable ------?<br />5. Where do you desire to go the most if we are allowed to travel abroad? Where?<br /><br />Session 2: Table topic questions （即席抽題演講）<br />Questions will be prepared and asked by the host during the session.<br /><br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔。<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<br /></span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Mar 05, 2021 10:26 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
